		<title>Taking a holiday.</title>
		<link>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/08/04/taking-a-holiday/</link>
					<comments>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/08/04/taking-a-holiday/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emi T]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 04 Aug 2014 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Basic info]]></category>
